Package: ebox-jabber
Architecture: all
Depends: ebox (>= 0.9.1), ebox (<< 0.9.99), ebox-firewall, ebox-usersandgroups (>= 0.7.0.99), jabber-common, jabberd2-ldap-bdb
Description: Instant messaging (Jabber)
 eBox is a framework for the development and deployment of security-wise
 network services in small and medium-sized networks, offering a simplified
 graphical interface to non expert users. It can be set up as a gateway,
 having some extra features over a usual router.
 .
 This module adds a Jabber server to your eBox installation, providing your 
 users with instant messaging.
